Package: goal
Type: Package
Title: GeOgraphical Analysis Library
Version: 1.0
Date: 2023-03-02
Authors@R: person( given ="Dimitris", family ="Kavroudakis", email="dimitris123@gmail.com", role=c("aut","cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5782-3049"))
Maintainer: Dimitris Kavroudakis <dimitris123@gmail.com>
Description: Library for the analysis of geographical data. Contains the following 4 group of functions:   
  (a) functions for the analysis of networks (`net`).   
  (b) functions for spatial-geometry conversions (`geo`).   
  (c) functions for geographical visualization and interpretation of statistics (`vis`).  
  (d) functions for analysis of UAV missions and flightpaths (`uav`).
  (e) functions for OpenStreetMap data analysis (`osm`).
